<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>17</hymn_number>
<title>PARDON, PEACE, AND POWER</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa ah I kipak ding um,
 A neihzawh dan sut un;
 A Thu sung ah ginna'n latsak,
 A tam zie ngaihtuoh un.

[V2]
 Ngaihdamna, muonna, hatna,
 Thienthona leh Pielgal a um;
 Cheng hih Isu vang in kei a,
 Pakna zaila chuh Amah kawm tung hen!

[V3]
 2. Pathien hehpihna chun gitloh,
 A ngaidam suokkei tai;
 Ngaihdamna, kichamna ka nei,
 Isu thisan chamna.

[V4]
 3. Hehpihna'n gitlohna zo di'n,
 Zawhna kim ei pie a;
 Lunggil ah Thagau Thiengtho chun,
 Gitloh A thiensak sek.

[V5]
 4. Pathien kawma mi puihna ding,
 Thagau in ei pie tai;
 Amah, Lal Krista ei piek khah,
 I lung u ah A cheng.

[V6]
 5. Ginna'n vangpiekna cheng chang in,
 Ginna naupangtak in;
 Pathien in Krista vang ngei in,
 Ei piek A tiem ahi.</lyrics>
</song>